was arrested at home 12 hours after the fire started at 340 am 
sunday used to work in a warehouse but had been unemployed for the 
past six months 
when questioned by police he broke down and cried and was 
remorseful odonnell said 
early sunday police said gonzalez went to the club and argued 
with his 45yearold former girlfriend before he was kicked out by 
a bouncer 
hes drinking at the club he wants to get back with her she 
