rebuke from the other palestinian leadership groups recently 
including the dominant fatah faction 
a twopage letter made available to the associated press 
criticized the group for actions that help nobody but the 
enemies 
it also charged that allowing disputes to break into the open 
will not help solve the problem but will lead to a civil war 
