technical efficiency 
international monitors expressed satisfaction with the votes 
fairness but the reporting of results has been an agonizing 
process 
east germany held the first free election among former soviet 
satellites on march 18 and provided projections of the outcome 
soon after polls closed provisional final results were available 
five hours after the last vote was cast and official results were 
announced the next morning 
