that japans tightly knit society can unravel itself only so fast 
many japanese are hesitant to disclose secrets to americans 
he says we came from companies with socalled lifetime 
employment we have complete trust in an employee because we know 
hes going to stay but here many people come and go and we think 
maybe hell give secrets to a competitor 
