the authority considers the device to be the most 
hazardous gaudiest most novel and most distracting advertising 
device on the thruway system and a flagrant violation of its 
regulations says a complaint issued by the agency 
the authority says the truck must go because it does not honor a 
660foot right of way for advertising next to the road 
